{
  "stem": "2581.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A young man came into that with that jacket to work, and I recognized it on him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, you see-- you see the back where this is-- you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all I did is ask him not to wear it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were preparing-- preparing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, my parents must have known more than what we were told.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then on-- on August 22, I think it was, because on the 24th we came to the-- to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Either the-- between the 22nd-- I don't remember the exact date.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The town was surrounded, and of course, Judenrats, they came to house-- to the house where we lived, in our grandfather's house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a two-year-old cousin that was-- had an appendix operation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was laying in the lounge chair in the alley between the houses the way it was in Europe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't bother to pick him up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They shot him right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all-- there were 65 people-- 65 people that we were-- that-- from that-- we were all pushed down that main street in the ghetto, which was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in Jewish, we called it a tannery street because there were tanneries on that street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they started pushing us and rushing us all into the church.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was a distance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whoever couldn't walk, they would shoot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They shot my grandmother, my father's mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know, she couldn't-- I'm sure she could walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She was a strong woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was an old woman, but she could-- it must have been because I didn't see her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't see her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then my father's cousin-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] my father's uncle was a respected man in town.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
